high_descs: walk forwards to the table, then hang a right and walk to the kitchen sink
grab the yellow knife out of the kitchen sink
turn around and walk back over to face the left side of the kitchen table
slice up the lettuce on the table
place the knife down in front of the left plate on the kitchen table
grab a slice of lettuce off of the table
move to the right a bit and face the table again
place the lettuce slice on the plate on the left
pick up the plate with the lettuce on it
turn around and walk over to the fridge in front of you
place the plate down inside of the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a slice of lettuce on a place down inside of the fridge

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink.
Grab the knife that is in the sink.
Turn and go to the table.
Face the table where the lettuce is at on the table.
Slice the lettuce that is on the table.
Grab a slice of lettuce.
Move over so you are in front of the plates on the table.
Place the slice of lettuce on the plate on the left and to the left of the knife on the plate.
Pick up the plate with the lettuce on it.
Go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the plate on the top shelf to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Slice lettuce to put on a plate.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the sink.
Pick the yellow-handled knife up out of the sink.
Turn around and take the knife to the wooden table.
Use the knife to slice the lettuce into seven thin slices, leaving the base of the lettuce in tact.
Stab the tip of the knife into the wooden table, in front of the gray plate closest to the lettuce. Leave the knife there.
Pick up the seventh lettuce slice from the right.
Move one step to your right to line up with the gray plate closest to the lettuce.
Put the lettuce slice onto the gray plate closest to the rest of the lettuce.
Pick up the plate containing the lettuce slice.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the plate inside, on the same shelf as the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a plate with a slice of lettuce on it into the fridge.
